’Щ@801b134e3ab0e4b5efa2f3386151ffd695ada5a4cb684b394d6d081f2c5f4c3fЩУTitle: title: polars integer
Path: Parameters
Content:
``base``
: An integer or expression representing the base (radix) of the number system (default is 10).
``dtype``
: Data type to cast to (defaults is i64).
